OL,5, Former MP Alice Mahon died of a cancer 
OL,6, linked to asbestos exposure. Now her   
OL,7, son is calling for asbestos to be      
OL,8, removed from all buildings to protect  
OL,9, lives.                                 
OL,11,FAsbestos is a material which if inhaled
OL,12,Fcan cause cancer and is the biggest    
OL,13,Fcause of work-related deaths in the UK.
OL,15,FMrs Mahon, who died last year of       
OL,16,Fmalignant mesothelioma at the age of   
OL,17,F85, was best known as a fiery Labour   
OL,18,Fleft-winger and a close ally of former 
OL,19,FLabour leader Jeremy Corbyn.           
